node.text:
Sensei Cindy Seah has spent close to 40 years of her life being a kick-ass karate practitioner.

The 60-year-old karate instructor shares her smooth moves, as well has her not-so-smooth journey in mastering and imparting the martial art.

#LegitOld. (This video was filmed in February, ahead of the implementation of the circuit breaker measures.)
